data.description: Description The Bisque Seta Radiator has large diameter tubing, which creates a robust and contemporary look. Rounded 'pepper pot' tops add character to the Seta Radiator, a highly practical and efficient design from Bisque. Deluxe air vent in matching finish included. Materials & Finishes The Bisque Seta Radiator is available in white, matt black, metallica and chrome finishes. Please note The chrome finish reduces radiator output 20% Additional information The Bisque Seta Radiator is available in several sizes and various colours if you require a specific size or colour not shown on the website please view the Bisque Seta Radiator Once you have found the size you require please email customerservices@nest.co.uk with the size you would like and a member of our sales team will be able to help you with your request.

data.name: Corner TV
data.description:
The Indian Jali Dark range is another extensive range in solid Sheesham hardwood with over 30 pieces in the range. The range is finished with wrought iron handles and portculis iron work and finished in a darker brown contrast and is a darker alternative to the normal Indian Jali range of lighter/medium browns.
The Thacket style gives a truly warm look to any home with its traditional clean lines to create a stylish look. There are many items to choose from including CD towers, coffee tables, dining room furniture and various occasional items.
Throughout the range you will find that all of the pieces compliment each other, and there is a wide variety to choose from to furnish your home.

data.name: Corner Wardrobe
data.description: This amazing corner wardrobe has a huge amount of storage space for clothes, shoes, books and toys. The unique shape enables the wardrobe to fit in the corner of the room and the constructions ensures that the wardrobe will not expand or shrink due to the effects of the weather - the back panels are made from a single piece so connector strips are no longer required (H201xW130xD94cm). Delivery time is approximately 4 weeks.

data.name: Corner chaise
data.description: The Amix is available to buy online and in store. The standard corner chaise is supplied with luxury foam and fibre seat interiors, in classic back style, in cover: scopo natural. The feet are in dark wood. Other foot options such as chrome effect feet are available on request. Other colours can also be ordered in store. Please note: the red scatter cushions are for display only. For easy access, the feet are detachable on all pieces. The corner chaise is supplied in two sections. This model has fully removable dry clean only covers. Please make sure you follow the manufacturer"s recommendations. As part of our Premier Delivery Service your furniture will be unwrapped and placed in position by our professionally trained delivery team.

data.name: Blackheath corner sofa (with corner table optional) Corner table
data.description: Features: Removable cushion covers for easy cleaning. Seams double-stitchedfor strength and neatness. Corner table has clear glass top. Available in leather or soft cover. Please note, a bespoke service is available on this corner sofa. Construction: Hardwood frame with resin-bonded panels. Heavy duty elasticated webbing suspension. high density foam overlay to soften the edges. Easy care Reflex foam seats and comfy Quallofill fibre backs. Customers Own Material (COM) If you prefer to have your sofa upholstered in an alternative fabric, let us know and we will work out a quote for you. Visit our showroom to see our wide range of Designers Guild fabrics / Romo / Linwood / Osbourne and Little etc. You can also supply your own - please speak to a member of staff.

data.name: Corner unit

data.name: Corner chaise
data.description: The Amix is available to buy online and in store. The standard corner chaise is supplied with luxury foam and fibre seat interiors, in classic back style, in cover: scopo natural. The feet are in dark wood. Other foot options such as chrome effect feet are available on request. Other colours can also be ordered in store. Please note: the red scatter cushions are for display only. For easy access, the feet are detachable on all pieces. The corner chaise is supplied in two sections. This model has fully removable dry clean only covers. Please make sure you follow the manufacturer"s recommendations. As part of our Premier Delivery Service your furniture will be unwrapped and placed in position by our professionally trained delivery team.

data.name: Corner Desk
data.description:
The Hereford Oak is a range of high quality modern lounge, office and bedroom furniture made from American white Oak. Simple, contemporary furniture and designed and styled for the UK, the natural beauty of this furniture will complement any home and each item is hand built using the age old skill of the artisan.
The furniture is constructed to the highest standards using only solid wood, dovetailed drawers, solid oak tongue and grooved drawer bottoms and back panels. Oak is loved for its strength, durability and beauty and this is further enhanced with a satin lacquer, giving a smooth, gentle sheen and revealing the natural beauty of the grain and colour.
See options for all the choices including great home office products.

Now you have the choice of metal or oak handles! Please specify in comments box on ordering!
